                <note rend="inline" type="source">816.48/75: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Chargé in Salvador</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Arnold</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Acting Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">San Salvador</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1919-04-28T17:00:00-05:56">
                            <hi rend="italic">April 28, 1919, 5 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                        <lb/>[<hi rend="italic">Received April 29, 12.30 a.m.</hi>]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Martial law declared today. Damage much greater than first anticipated. Number of
                    deaths at present reported 40 persons. Notify Weinberg’s parents Washington he
                    is safe.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Arnold</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
